wminc-code-macrolanguage: [[wikipedia:$2 language|"$3" language]] la anɛ [[wikipedia:ISO 639 macrolanguage|macrolanguage]],ka mɔr pian'ad banɛ dɔl la nwa:
wminc-code-collective: Koot kanɛ an "$1" la pʋ bɛɛ tis pian'ad yinne si'aa,amaa ka bɛɛ tis pian'ad gum sieba ka li yʋ'ʋr an ye [[wikipedia:$2 language|"$3" languages]]
wminc-code-retired: Pian'ad kaŋa koot la tiak ya ka pʋ lɛm bɛ tis Pin'ilʋg pian'ad la.
wminc-custom-editnotice-2: A-nyaŋi pa'an pian'ad banɛ ka fʋ nyaŋi nɔk tʋm la,bɛllimnɛ nɔkim $1 nwa tʋm. Tituunli, fʋ buudi pian'ad ya'a anɛ Kʋsaal ka fʋ na nyaŋi pian' Na'asaal sʋ'ʋŋa, nɔkim $2 tʋm

wminc-custom-featuredwikis-active: Bama vʋe bɛɛ tʋm ka li kʋ yuugɛ ba na di'e ba mɛŋ zin'ig:
wminc-custom-newarticletext-noprefix: Bɛllimnɛ baŋim: fʋ maan nɛ lakir ka [[$1|prefix]] kae.
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-3: Fʋ maan nɛ ([[$1|prefixed]])lakir paal ka li yʋ'ʋr an "{{FULLPAGENAME}}".
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-4: Mɛ Paasim prefixes nam tisi fʋ link nam nwa: [[Page title]] to [[Wx/xx/Page title]] and {{Page title}} to {{Wx/xx/Page title}}.
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-5: A-maal Nɛ'ɛŋa sʋ'ʋŋaa, fʋ tʋn'e zaŋ [[$1|Add prefix gate]] niŋ
wminc-custom-tb-incorrect-title-title: Fʋ mɔɔd ye fʋ maal lakir nɛ yʋ'ʋgbɛlʋŋ
wminc-custom-tb-incorrect-title-text:
Saŋa pamm yʋ'ʋr la pʋ mɔr [[$1|prefix]] bɛɛ di bɛnɛ suosi'a kanɛ mɔr gbɛlʋŋ ( banɛ mɔr vubiel bɛda bɛ prefix ni, nɛ trailing slash nɛ banɛ bɛ.).
Fʋ ya'a yinɛ zin'isi'a ke kpɛ' na,bɛllimnɛ lɛm ti maal link la ka yʋ'ʋn maal lakir ka li yʋ'ʋr dɔl tituaa. Fʋ ya'a mɔɔd nɛ ye kpa maal lakir la, bɛllimnɛ maalim lakir la li yʋ'ʋr dɔl bɛɛ tu'al tituaa.
Ka saŋa kanɛ ka nɛ'ɛŋa gu'udif ka fʋ kʋ nyaŋi maal lakir si'a kanɛ ka fʋ mi' sʋ'ʋŋa ye li mɔr yʋ'ʋr kanɛ an tituaa, bɛllimnɛ [[$2|kɛl ka Kpɛɛmnam baŋi li yɛla]].
wminc-custom-tb-invalid-code-title: Fʋ mɔɔd nɛ ye fʋ maal lakir kanɛ ka [[$1|ISO 639-1 bɛɛ -3 koot]] kanɛ tʋm kae
wminc-custom-tb-invalid-code-text:
Koot kaŋa pʋ tʋmma bɛɛ ka'a nɛ pian'ad kanɛ siak Wikipedia tʋʋm paala bʋnnɛ.
Fʋ ya'a yinɛ lakir si'a ni ke kpɛ' na,bɛllimnɛ lɛm ti maal link la ka nyaan maal lakir kanɛ yʋ'ʋri dɔl tituaa la.

ka li ya'a ti anɛ ye nɛ'ɛŋa gu'udif suor ka fʋ kʋ nyaŋi maal lakir si'a kanɛ ka fʋ tɛn'ɛs ye li mɔr koot ISO 639-3 bɛɛ -3 koot kanɛ tʋm bɛɛ an pian'ad kanɛ ka ba siak di'e, bɛllimnɛ [[$1|kɛl ka Kpɛɛmnam baŋi li yɛla ]]
gadget-addprefix: Add prefix: Zaŋim prefixes nam paas link namin saŋa kanɛ ka fʋ maan lakir.
wminc-gadget-addprefix-help: Di pʋ lɛn nar ye fʋ mɔr prefix la niŋid ya'asa fʋ ya'a ti dɛmisid lakir kaŋaa. Li mɛŋ na paas fʋ ya'a zaŋ lakir kaŋa pa'al sɔ' wʋsa.
wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-text: Nɔkim gbaʋŋ kaŋa n paas interwiki linknam dɔlisid wikidata laʋkin. Kʋdʋm nɔkim wikidata laʋk ID bɛɛ URL labil laʋk si'a bɛɛ sɔbʋg kanɛ dɛŋim maal bɛ pian'asi'a ni n bɛ gbinnin nwa ka din "{{int:wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-publish}}"
